Situated in the heart of the central south business district, approximately 11kms from the heart of the Brisbane CBD. The property sits strategically within minutes to Beaudesert Rd and SEQ’s major arterial links.
-	1,172sqm GFA
-	932sqm clear span warehouse with up to 7.65m internal height
-	240sqm air-conditioned office space over two levels 
-	Access via multiple container height roller doors 
-	300 amps of 3 phase power 
-	Fully fenced and secure site 

For further information or to arrange an inspection please contact CBRE.
